text: Rafael Ylönen (26 November 1906 - 31 March 1997) was a Finnish gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Finnish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lappeenranta
